Non-free Licenses非自由许可证

What are Non-Free, Free, and Open Source licenses?什么是非免费、免费和开源许可证？

A non-free license is one that does not meet the Free Software Definition or the Open Source Definition. ContentDB will clearly label any packages with non-free licenses, and they will be subject to limited promotion.非自由许可证是不符合自由软件定义或开源定义的许可证。 ContentDB 将清楚地标记任何带有非自由许可证的包，并且它们将受到有限的促销。

How does ContentDB deal with Non-Free Licenses?ContentDB 如何处理非自由许可证？

ContentDB does not allow certain non-free licenses, and will limit the promotion of packages with non-free licenses.ContentDB 不允许某些非自由许可，并将限制使用非自由许可的软件包的推广。

Minetest is free and open source software, and is only as big as it is now because of this. It's pretty amazing you can take nearly any published mod and modify it to how you like - add some features, maybe fix some bugs - and then share those modifications without the worry of legal issues. The project, itself, relies on open source contributions to survive - if it were non-free, then it would have died when celeron55 lost interest.Minetest 是免费的开源软件，因此才像现在这样大。令人惊奇的是，您几乎可以采用任何已发布的模组并将其修改为您喜欢的方式——添加一些功能，也许修复一些错误——然后共享这些修改而无需担心法律问题。该项目本身依赖于开源贡献来生存——如果它不是免费的，那么当 celeron55 失去兴趣时它就会死掉。

If you have played nearly any game with a large modding scene, you will find that most mods are legally ambiguous. A lot of them don't even provide the source code to allow you to bug fix or extend as you need.如果您玩过几乎所有具有大型模组场景的游戏，您会发现大多数模组在法律上都是模棱两可的。他们中的很多人甚至不提供源代码来让您根据需要修复或扩展错误。

Limiting the promotion of problematic licenses helps Minetest avoid ending up in such a state. Licenses that prohibit redistribution or modification are completely banned from ContentDB and the Minetest forums. Other non-free licenses will be subject to limited promotion - they won't be shown by default in the client.限制有问题的许可证的推广有助于 Minetest 避免陷入这种状态。 ContentDB 和 Minetest 论坛完全禁止禁止再分发或修改的许可证。其他非免费许可证将受到有限的推广——它们不会默认显示在客户端中。

Not providing full promotion on ContentDB, or not allowing your package at all, doesn't mean you can't make such content - it just means we're not going to help you spread it.不在 ContentDB 上提供全面宣传，或者根本不允许您的包裹，并不意味着您不能制作此类内容——这只是意味着我们不会帮助您传播它。

What's so bad about licenses that forbid commercial use?禁止商业使用的许可证有什么不好？

Please read reasons not to use a Creative Commons -NC license. Here's a quick summary related to Minetest content:请阅读不使用 Creative Commons -NC 许可证的原因。以下是与 Minetest 内容相关的快速摘要：

  1. They make your work incompatible with a growing body of free content, even if you do want to allow derivative works or combinations. This means that it can cause problems when another modder wishes to include your work in a modpack or game.它们使您的作品与越来越多的免费内容不兼容，即使您确实希望允许衍生作品或组合。这意味着当另一个模组作者希望将您的作品包含在模组包或游戏中时，它可能会导致问题。
  2. They may rule out other basic and beneficial uses that you want to allow. For example, CC -NC will forbid showing your content in a monetised YouTube video.他们可能会排除您想要允许的其他基本和有益用途。例如，CC -NC 将禁止在获利的 YouTube 视频中显示您的内容。
  3. They are unlikely to increase the potential profit from your work, and a share-alike license serves the goal to protect your work from unethical exploitation equally well.它们不太可能增加您工作的潜在利润，并且类似共享许可的目标是同样有效地保护您的工作免受不道德的剥削。

How can I show non-free packages in the client?如何在客户端中显示非免费包？

Non-free packages are hidden in the client by default, partly in order to comply with the rules of various Linux distributions.非自由软件包默认隐藏在客户端中，部分原因是为了遵守各种 Linux 发行版的规则。

Users can opt-in to showing non-free software, if they wish:如果愿意，用户可以选择显示非自由软件：

  1. In the main menu, go to Settings > All settings在主菜单中，转到设置 > 所有设置
  2. Search for "ContentDB Flag Blacklist".搜索“ContentDB 标记黑名单”。
  3. Edit that setting to remove nonfree,.编辑该设置以删除 nonfree，。

The platform_default flag is used to control what content each platforms shows. It doesn't hide anything on Desktop, but hides all mature content on Android. You may wish to remove all text from that setting completely, leaving it blank. See Content Warnings for information on mature content.platform_default 标志用于控制每个平台显示的内容。它不会在桌面上隐藏任何内容，但会在 Android 上隐藏所有成人内容。您可能希望从该设置中完全删除所有文本，将其留空。有关成人内容的信息，请参阅内容警告。
